## What Results Can I Expect from Internal Linking?

Internal linking improvements typically show ranking impacts within 4-12 weeks as search engines recrawl and re-evaluate page authority. Pages receiving concentrated linking attention often gain 3-10 position improvements for target queries.

The most significant improvements occur on pages with quality content but poor linking integration. Adding strategic internal links unlocks ranking potential that existing content quality warrants but structural isolation previously prevented.

